videos.headline: Stanford strikes first with 18-yard TD pass
videos.description: K.J. Costello throws on target to JJ Arcega-Whiteside, who makes the catch in the end zone to give the Cardinal an early 7-0 lead over the Cougars.

videos.headline: Washington State responds with 5-yard TD run
videos.description: RB James Williams gets through a hole and finds paydirt to even the score at 7-7 against the Cardinal.

videos.headline: Washington State breaks through for strip-sack
videos.description: LB Peyton Pelleur jars the ball free from K.J. Costello, and DL Taylor Comfort falls on it to set the Cougars up inside the Cardinal 25-yard line.

videos.headline: Cougars jump ahead with 4-yard TD pass
videos.description: Gardner Minshew swings it out to a wide-open Max Borghi, who walks into the end zone and makes it 14-7 Washington State.

videos.headline: Love's 43-yard scamper leads to another Cardinal TD
videos.description: Bryce Love charges down the sideline to the Cougars' 20-yard line, and Cameron Scarlett finishes the drive a few plays later with a 2-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Stanford reclaims lead with 10-yard TD pass
videos.description: K.J. Costello tosses one to TE Kaden Smith after the play-action fake, and the Cardinal jump back in front 21-14.

videos.headline: Stanford converts on 4th-and-goal to double lead
videos.description: K.J. Costello connects with FB Houston Heimuli in the flat for an easy pitch-and-catch score to make it 28-14 Cardinal over the Cougars.

videos.headline: Cougars set up FG with 54-yard catch-and-run
videos.description: Gardner Minshew finds Jamire Calvin over the middle, who breaks a tackle and gets all the way to the Cardinal 13-yard line to set up a Cougars' field goal at the end of the 1st half.

videos.headline: Washington State trims lead with 3-yard TD run
videos.description: RB James Williams makes the extra effort and powers his way across the goal line to cut Stanford's lead to 28-24.

videos.headline: Washington State ties it up with 7-yard TD pass
videos.description: Gardner Minshew threads the needle to Davontavean Martin, who makes a leaping grab to knot the score at 31-31.

videos.headline: Washington State takes lead late in 4th quarter
videos.description: Gardner Minshew throws a 3-yard strike to Renard Bell on the out-route, giving the Cougars a 38-31 lead with less than 5 minutes to play.

videos.headline: Stanford scores equalizer with 25-yard TD
videos.description: K.J. Costello throws a dart to JJ Arcega-Whiteside, who makes a lunging grab and ties the score at 38-38 with just 1:25 left.

videos.headline: Minshew sets up go-ahead FG with 35-yard strike
videos.description: Gardner Minshew goes deep down the middle to find Jamire Calvin, who brings it in and sets up Blake Mazza's go-ahead field goal.
